    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my awesome car. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out for a weekend getaway, it\u2019s ready to go and looks fantastic. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have! Come see it for yourself\u2014it's a total gem!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
